=======================
Virtual LAVA laboratory
=======================

Get your own LAVA laboratory up and running in no time.

Getting started
---------------

Prerequisites
~~~~~~~~~~~~~

* VirtualBox_
* Vagrant_
* Ansible_

.. _VirtualBox: https://www.virtualbox.org/wiki/Downloads
.. _Vagrant: https://www.vagrantup.com/downloads.html
.. _Ansible: http://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/intro_installation.html

Running
~~~~~~~

.. code:: sh

    vagrant up


Tested environment
------------------

========== ================
Ubuntu     16.04 ("Xenial")
VirtualBox 5.1.30
Vagrant    2.0.1
Ansible    2.4.1.0
========== ================
